data.text:
Oh geez, I even forgot Luke's new favorite one-liners:
"Impressive. Every word in that sentence was wrong"
"Amazing. Every word of what you just said was wrong"

It's so cheesy, I love it. I wanna use those lines in real life and see if anyone would catch the reference.

@SoushinSen My biggest gripe with the film is that it takes all the setup form the previous movie and throws it all away. Who is Snoke, how strong is he and why is he important? Doesn't matter I guess. They telegraphed a KOTOR double turn for Rey and Kylo, but toss it out too.
